  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Purchase Executive",
  "description": "<p>Be part of our ongoing expansion, we're in search of a cheerful individual with initiative and strong integrity who is interested in learning the ropes of running an ecommerce business.</p><p>In this unique job opportunity, we distinguish ourselves by prioritizing the perfect fit for each employee, setting us apart from other employers. As a result, we have achieved substantial growth compared to our competitors. Join us and be part of a team that values your unique strengths and fosters your professional journey.<br /></p><p>Job Responsibilities:</p><p>• Source and evaluate new suppliers for cost, quality, lead time, and reliability.</p><p>• Maintain strong relationships with existing suppliers: negotiate pricing, MOQ, terms, and delivery schedules.</p><p>• Handle day-to-day supplier communications (quotations, order confirmation, shipment updates, issue resolution).</p><p>• Monitor stock levels and replenish based on sales trends, forecasts, and campaign schedules.</p><p>• Coordinate with warehouse/operations on inbound planning, receiving, and stock accuracy.</p><p>• Prepare purchasing reports (weekly/monthly): fast movers, slow movers, reorder suggestions, and budget tracking.<br /></p><p>Requirements:</p><p>• Good communication and negotiation skills.</p><p>• Ability to think strategically while executing creatively and efficiently.</p><p>• Able to multi-task and work in a fast-paced environment.</p><p>• Good team player, yet independent with minimum supervision.<br /></p><p>Benefits:</p><p>• Performance Bonus</p><p>• Employee Awards</p><p>• Medical Benefits<br /></p><p>Working Days:</p><p>• 5.5 days<br /></p><p>Working Hours</p><p>• 8:00 am – 5:00 pm (Monday to Friday)</p><p>• 8:00am – 12pm (Saturday)<br /></p><p>Location:</p><p>• Woodlands, Singapore<br /></p><p>If you're a go-getter with a sunny disposition and you're ready to embark on a rewarding journey with us, don't hesitate to get in touch!</p>",
